<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 01 00 00 00 00">你没必要<delay8 />那么客气地招待我，<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我和你可是铁哥们儿啊！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 01 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我就随便坐了，<delay8 />
你别介意啊！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 01 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Pardon" target="actor" targetSpec="" />诶～<delay frames="30" />
原来你喜欢这样子风格的房间啊？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我也挺喜欢的！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 01 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这一看<delay8 />我就知道<delay20 />
是<tag a="110" b="3" />你的房间！<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />虽然不知道为什么这么觉得！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 01 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />每次进别人家门的时候，<delay20 />
多少会有点紧张呢<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但来你家的时候<delay8 />就不会，<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你家真是个神奇的地方。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="006" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />每次被朋友叫到家里玩的时候，<delay frames="30" />
都会感觉到关系更加好了，<delay20 />
所以很开心呢！<pageBreak /><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />虽然<delay8 />今天<delay20 />
是我硬要来的<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="007" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Aha" target="actor" targetSpec="" />诶～<delay20 />原来<tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd00" />的
房间是这种感觉的啊！<pageBreak /><anim id="Restless" target="actor" targetSpec="" />没想到，<delay20 />这家伙还挺有品位的<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="30" />
<anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我也不能输啊！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="008" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />呐，<delay20 /><tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd00" />那家伙<delay8 />
是不是在偷笑？<pageBreak /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />自从我们到这儿来玩以后，<delay8 />
那家伙就一直那个表情<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="101" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="101_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你以后想布置成什么样的房间，<delay20 />
现在有想法了吗？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="101_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />诶！<delay20 />
这房间里<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 /><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />什么也没有啊。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="101_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这房间布置得很简洁嘛！<delay20 />
难道你是<delay8 />那个？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就是，<delay frames="30" />那个<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" /><anim id="IdeaBulb" target="actor" targetSpec="" />极简<delay frames="40" />主义？<delay20 /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
</msbt>